WEBVTT

00:00.830 --> 00:02.000
《越狱》  前情回顾
Previously on Prison Break.

00:03.060 --> 00:06.160
如果"锡拉"是一张饼  我们只拿到其中一块
If Scylla was like a pizza, all we got is a slice.

00:06.230 --> 00:07.930
"锡拉"不是一张卡
So Scylla isn't one card.

00:08.000 --> 00:09.430
是六张
It's six.

00:09.500 --> 00:11.800
这事发生多久了
How long has  it been happening?

00:11.860 --> 00:12.860
这不是大问题
It's not a big deal.

00:12.930 --> 00:13.960
你13岁的时候  就已是个大问题了
It was a big deal when you were 13.

00:14.030 --> 00:15.560
迈克尔和你说过妈的事吗
Michael told you about Mom?

00:15.630 --> 00:18.400
-没有  -她小时候经常流鼻血
No. As a kid, she got nosebleeds.

00:18.460 --> 00:20.630
她30多岁时  又开始流鼻血
In her 30s, they started up again.

00:20.700 --> 00:22.130
你母亲什么时候去世的
How old was your mom when she passed away?

00:22.200 --> 00:25.100
31岁  迈克尔也刚好31岁
31. Michael's just turning 31.

00:25.160 --> 00:27.700
那个人是谁
Who's that?

00:27.760 --> 00:28.860
他就是杀我儿子的凶手
That's the man that killed my son.

00:40.760 --> 00:42.230
他就象个数码黑洞
It's like a digital black hole.

00:42.300 --> 00:44.760
能接收10英尺内的所有电子数据
It swallows up any electronic data within ten feet.

00:46.530 --> 00:47.330
格兰先生
Mr. Glenn?

00:47.400 --> 00:48.800
我们有麻烦了
We got a problem.

00:48.860 --> 00:50.130
那是干什么用的
What's that do?

00:50.200 --> 00:51.540
是个电子游戏机的
It's a battery pack

00:51.540 --> 00:52.330
电池组
for a video game console.

00:54.030 --> 00:56.100
那你只能买个新的了
You'll need to buy a new one.

00:57.330 --> 00:59.230
锡拉  明天给我的话
Scylla. Get it to me by tomorrow

00:59.300 --> 01:01.300
你就能拿原来报酬的一半
and you will receive 50% of the fee.

01:01.360 --> 01:04.160
后天  四分之一
Two days, 25%.

01:04.230 --> 01:05.730
大后天
Three days,

01:05.800 --> 01:07.000
我让你脑袋开花
I shoot you through the brain.

01:10.730 --> 01:12.660
你是谁
Who is this?

01:12.730 --> 01:14.660
你好  迈克尔
Hello, Michael.

01:28.160 --> 01:29.460
你明白吧
You know what?

01:29.530 --> 01:31.300
如果格莱布再给我找这样的烂活
If Crab ever throws a psycho at us like this again,

01:31.360 --> 01:33.000
我就宰了他
I'm going to kill him.

01:33.060 --> 01:35.530
对  但是我们如果不干的话  格莱布会宰了我们
Yeah, but if we don't get this psycho, Crab's going to kill us.

01:35.600 --> 01:37.000
把枪准备好
Just have the burner ready.

01:37.060 --> 01:38.830
准备好了
Got it covered.

01:42.130 --> 01:44.430
做完这个之后  我就洗手不干了
After this job, I'm done, man.

01:44.500 --> 01:46.160
我不能再做下去了
I can't do this anymore.

01:46.230 --> 01:49.030
你觉得格莱布会怎么说
What do you think Crab will say about that?

01:49.100 --> 01:51.200
我不管他说什么
I don't care what Crab says about that.

01:51.260 --> 01:54.130
如果进监狱的话  我还怎么做个好父亲
How can I be a good father if I'm always in prison?

01:54.200 --> 01:57.700
我错过了我孩子的童年
I missed out on my kid's childhood.

01:57.760 --> 01:59.630
我不能再错过他成长的过程
I'm not going to miss out on him becoming a man.

01:59.700 --> 02:04.460
说实话  就算是你干  这个计划也太大胆了
You know, not for nothing, but this plan is crazy even for you.

02:04.530 --> 02:06.030
你确定这是唯一办法
You sure this is the only way?

02:06.100 --> 02:07.200
没错
Yeah.

02:08.530 --> 02:10.830
快看  他出来了
Hey look. He's coming out.

02:10.900 --> 02:12.830
他带着箱子
He's got the case.

02:14.800 --> 02:16.030
系好安全带
Let's buckle up.

02:44.000 --> 02:45.730
把手举起来  把手举起来
Put your hands up! Put your hands up!

02:59.160 --> 03:00.100
别客气
You're welcome.

03:00.160 --> 03:02.230
快闪
Let's go!

03:09.360 --> 03:11.260
等等  这就是你的好主意
So wait a minute. This is your brilliant plan?

03:11.330 --> 03:14.860
你打算用自杀的方法去撞将军的车
You're going to pull a kamikaze mission on the General's car?

03:15.760 --> 03:17.400
你的仪器已经没了
Now that the device is gone,

03:17.460 --> 03:19.200
你的意见也就不重要了
your opinion doesn't matter.

03:19.260 --> 03:20.800
闭嘴  加你的油
So shut up and pump.

03:22.060 --> 03:24.530
我们知道将军总是轻装行动
We know the General travels light.

03:24.600 --> 03:26.230
一辆轿车  几个保镖
One limo and a couple of guards.

03:26.300 --> 03:27.860
我不担心那几个保镖  我担心的是撞车
It ain't the guards I'm worried about; it's the crash.

03:27.930 --> 03:30.600
我没说过这会很轻松
Look, I never said this was going to be easy.

03:44.300 --> 03:45.900
别激动
Just relax.

03:49.860 --> 03:52.660
首先  巴拿马的事是公事公办
First off, Panama was a job.

03:52.730 --> 03:54.060
日后再算账
Some other time.

03:54.130 --> 03:55.300
你要“锡拉“做什么
What do you want with Scylla?

03:55.360 --> 03:56.400
那是我自己的事
That's my business.

03:56.460 --> 03:57.900
我们不是在巴拿马
We're not in Panama anymore,

03:57.960 --> 04:00.230
我也不在监狱里  我再问一次
and I'm not behind a fence, so, again,

04:00.300 --> 04:01.730
你要“锡拉”做什么
what do you want with Scylla?

04:01.800 --> 04:04.030
和你一样  打垮公司
Same thing you want: bring down the Company.

04:04.100 --> 04:05.530
很好  那你何不
Great. Then why don't you

04:05.600 --> 04:07.360
把缺的几页纸给我  然后消失呢
give me those missing pages and disappear?

04:07.430 --> 04:09.230
我很想那么做  你记得那天
I'd love to. You remember that day

04:09.300 --> 04:11.460
我们在罗斯福酒店  惠斯勒复制了Lief的卡
at the Roosevelt when Whistler made off with Lief's card?

04:11.530 --> 04:13.630
你觉得是谁的主意
Who do you think took the fall for that?

04:13.700 --> 04:16.160
我们的名字都在同一张黑名单里
Our names are at the top of the same hit list.

04:16.230 --> 04:18.330
我不知道你们有什么协议
Now, I don't know what arrangement you two have,

04:18.400 --> 04:19.800
我需要一些资金
but I need some traveling money.

04:19.860 --> 04:21.030
我们过会再谈这个
Let's talk about that later.

04:21.100 --> 04:22.330
我们干嘛不谈谈你是在给
Why don't we talk about the kind of scum

04:22.400 --> 04:23.900
什么样的烂人付钱
you're willing to put on the payroll?

04:23.960 --> 04:25.860
告诉我一个用不到她的理由  我听你的
Give me a way to do it without her, and we'll do it.

04:25.930 --> 04:27.330
我们需要那些纸
We need the pages.

04:28.860 --> 04:31.200
这是个交易
It's a package deal.

04:31.260 --> 04:33.030
我们是拍档了吗
Are we partners?

04:36.500 --> 04:38.030
拍档
Partners.

04:47.860 --> 04:50.230
我刚刚往机器里投了一个币
Look, I barely dropped a nickel in the slots, right?

04:50.300 --> 04:51.500
那人就过来了
This guy was all...

04:51.560 --> 04:52.630
我们真应该打死你
We ought to blanket party your ass.

04:52.700 --> 04:54.560
那个仪器呢
Where's the device?

04:54.630 --> 04:56.700
-能不能拿回来  -快说
Can it be salvaged? Tell him.

05:00.660 --> 05:02.400
赌台老板把它收走了
Pit boss walked off with it.

05:02.460 --> 05:06.030
那好  我们只能让你提前退休了
Okay. Well, we're going to call this your early retirement.

05:06.100 --> 05:07.560
你要么上楼
You can either go upstairs

05:07.630 --> 05:10.200
坐在你的小床上  等我们把事情解决
and sit on your cot and ride out the rest of this thing,

05:10.260 --> 05:11.560
否则  我就给赛尔夫探员打电话
or I can call Agent Self

05:11.630 --> 05:13.700
那你就能慢慢享受刑期了
and you can ride out the rest of your prison sentence.

05:13.760 --> 05:15.400
你选吧
Your choice.

05:31.130 --> 05:32.930
我要和你谈谈
I need to talk to you.

05:36.100 --> 05:38.360
你哥哥说了你流鼻血的事
So your brother told me about your nosebleeds.

05:38.430 --> 05:40.880
他还说了你妈妈的情况
And he told me about your mom.

05:40.880 --> 05:41.530
那不是他该做的
That wasn't his place.

05:41.600 --> 05:43.430
为你担心
To be worried about you?

05:43.500 --> 05:47.030
妈妈得病时  林肯每天都在医院  握着她的手
When Mom got sick, Linc was at the hospital every day, holding her hand,

05:47.100 --> 05:49.760
看着妈妈去世  他那时才13岁
watching her die, and he was 13.

05:49.830 --> 05:52.030
这件事改变了他  让他对任何事都过头担心
It changed him. It made him overprotective.

05:52.100 --> 05:53.030
现在他开始
And now he's jumping

05:53.100 --> 05:54.130
用错误的原因
to all the wrong conclusions

05:54.200 --> 05:55.360
得出错误的结论
for all the wrong reasons,

05:55.430 --> 05:57.200
而且都无中生有的
and it's... it's over nothing because

05:57.260 --> 05:58.900
我很好
I'm fine.

05:58.960 --> 06:01.730
你看起来可不好
You don't look fine.

06:01.800 --> 06:07.710
因为我也有些事情要告诉你
Well, maybe that's because there's something I have to tell you.

06:11.130 --> 06:12.700
格雷琴还活着
Gretchen's alive.

