06:43.200 --> 06:46.160
《越狱》第四季 第八集
Prison.Break.S04E08

06:55.600 --> 06:58.330
她和帝博格一起合作
She's working with T-Bag,

06:58.400 --> 07:00.800
他们有几张惠斯勒的鸟类书页
and they have several pages from Whistler's bird book,

07:00.860 --> 07:02.830
他们也想加入找锡拉
and they want in on Scylla.

07:02.900 --> 07:06.830
我们说话的同时  赛尔夫正和他们谈条件
Self is cutting them a deal as we speak.

07:08.060 --> 07:11.060
赛尔夫知道他们有自己的计划
Self knows that they have their own agenda,

07:11.130 --> 07:12.500
但我们也有
but so do we

07:12.560 --> 07:14.400
只要我们拿到那几页纸
and as soon as we get those pages back,

07:14.460 --> 07:16.600
格雷琴和帝博格就会为他们做的事付出代价
Gretchen and T-Bag are going to pay for everything.

07:16.660 --> 07:18.730
他们会得到应有的惩罚
They're going to get exactly what's coming to them.

07:25.860 --> 07:28.060
整件事情和格雷琴无关
This isn't about Gretchen.

07:28.130 --> 07:29.830
也不会牵扯私人恩怨
It's not about any one person.

07:29.900 --> 07:33.230
我们必须结束这一切
And we... we have to finish it.

07:37.530 --> 07:39.130
我想自己呆一会
I need a minute.

07:40.560 --> 07:42.230
可以吗
Please.

08:22.030 --> 08:23.460
我绝对不相信
I can't believe this!

08:23.530 --> 08:24.830
我们有其他选择吗
What choice do we have?

08:24.900 --> 08:26.260
格雷琴加入我们
Gretchen's on the team.

08:26.330 --> 08:27.460
不管喜不喜欢
Like it or not,

08:27.530 --> 08:29.100
我们需要那几页纸
we need those pages.

08:29.160 --> 08:30.000
我们要和这婊子[西班牙语]合作
Another perra we're jumping in bed with?

08:30.060 --> 08:31.460
对我们来说不是第一次了
Not exactly new territory for us.

08:31.530 --> 08:33.100
我不管我们要和谁合作
I don't care who we gotta partner up with.

08:33.160 --> 08:35.360
我们拿到那些纸  就才可以打入"公司"
We get those papers, we make with the break-in,

08:35.430 --> 08:36.830
就能完成任务
we get this job done.

08:36.900 --> 08:38.860
她也可能和"公司"还有联系  我不确定
She could still have ties to the Company, man. I don't know.

08:38.930 --> 08:41.600
到时候  我们再担心格雷琴
We'll worry about Gretchen when the time is right.

08:41.660 --> 08:44.400
现在  我们要集中在将军身上
For now, let's focus on the General.

08:46.630 --> 08:49.030
格雷琴加入我们也改变不了什么
This thing with Gretchen doesn't change a thing.

08:49.100 --> 08:50.800
我们
We're, uh...

08:50.860 --> 08:52.530
我们还是接近目标
we're still close.

08:52.600 --> 08:55.460
更接近"锡拉"  离怀特却更远了
Closer to Scylla, farther from Wyatt.

08:55.530 --> 08:57.930
这也说不准
You don't know that.

08:58.000 --> 08:59.300
先集中精力  好吗
Just stay focused, all right?

08:59.360 --> 09:01.260
这才是我要集中精力的地方
This is my focus, okay?

09:01.330 --> 09:04.460
我还是做我该做的事
I'm doing the job, okay? All right? All right?

09:04.530 --> 09:07.500
每一天  杀我儿子的凶手就离我更远
Every day, the trail to my son's killer gets a little bit colder.

09:08.730 --> 09:11.030
我能做的就只有集中精力
That's all I do is focus.

09:25.460 --> 09:27.030
你在干什么
What are you doing?

09:27.100 --> 09:29.230
只是
Um... It's just... uh...

09:29.300 --> 09:30.530
我们要把电脑拿楼下用
We're going to need that downstairs.

09:30.600 --> 09:34.400
那我就呆在这好了
Yeah. I'll just, uh... be up here.

10:14.990 --> 10:17.600
多少钱换斯科菲尔德和布伦斯
How much for Scofield and Burrows?

10:40.920 --> 10:43.920
我听说你们俩有了个协议
I see you two have come to an agreement.

10:43.980 --> 10:45.150
放了她 是因为她要工作
She's on work release,

10:45.220 --> 10:46.580
和你一样
just like you.

10:46.650 --> 10:48.150
什么样的工作
What kind of work?

10:48.220 --> 10:50.820
你和那个秘书在办公室里保守秘密
You and the secretary keep things quiet in the office

10:50.880 --> 10:52.420
迈克尔从隧道去找"锡拉"
while Michael tunnels to Scylla.

10:54.380 --> 10:55.480
你真的以为
You really think

10:55.550 --> 10:57.650
斯科菲尔德会遵守他的诺言
Scofield's gonna keep his word, huh?

10:59.020 --> 11:01.650
你把他爱的女人往死里打
You horsewhipped the woman he loves.

11:01.720 --> 11:03.820
迈克尔和我们一样想得到“锡拉”
Michael wants Scylla just as badly as we do.

11:03.880 --> 11:05.550
没错  他当时也想逃出监狱
Yeah, he wanted out of prison, too.

11:05.620 --> 11:09.180
我们的合作在那之后就结束了
Our partnership lasted long enough for that to happen,

11:09.250 --> 11:10.980
然后  我们就分道扬镳了
and then...  we parted ways.

11:11.050 --> 11:11.880
相信我
Trust me.

11:11.950 --> 11:13.980
先生  请进
Yeah, um, go on in, sir.

11:14.050 --> 11:16.350
斯科菲尔德会利用你
Scofield will use you

11:16.420 --> 11:19.220
为了给他女朋友报仇  他会在你背后来一刀
and then he's gonna bury the knife in your back for what you did to his lady friend.

11:24.050 --> 11:25.820
"锡拉"在哪
Where's Scylla?

11:25.880 --> 11:29.350
早上好  先生
Good morning to you, too, sir.

11:29.420 --> 11:30.350
先生们
Gentlemen.

11:30.420 --> 11:32.150
我给了你3天
I gave you three days.

11:32.220 --> 11:33.680
"锡拉"在哪
Where's Scylla?

11:36.450 --> 11:38.580
我
I...

11:38.650 --> 11:44.320
冯先生  别急着下结论
Now, uh, Mr. Feng, let's not do anything rash.

11:44.380 --> 11:46.220
你就是冯
So you're Feng.

11:46.280 --> 11:49.320
我们还没见过面
We haven't actually met in person.

11:49.380 --> 11:51.420
我就是"斑蛇行动"中
I was the liaison between the Company and your

11:51.480 --> 11:53.720
你的雇主和"公司"之间的联络人
Chinese employers on Operation Copperhead.

11:53.780 --> 11:56.320
苏珊
Susan?

11:56.380 --> 11:57.350
没错
That's right.

11:58.720 --> 12:00.180
你从为"公司"卖命
You went from working for the Company

12:00.250 --> 12:02.250
转变为盗取能摧毁他们的证据
to stealing the one thing that could destroy them.

12:02.320 --> 12:04.080
这个转变未免太突然了
That's a tight turn.

12:04.150 --> 12:06.150
从"锡拉"的价格来看
With a price that Scylla commands on the open market,

12:06.220 --> 12:07.150
任何人都会变
anybody would turn.

12:07.220 --> 12:09.280
顺便说一下  值200吧
Which is, by the way, 200.

12:13.450 --> 12:16.080
我们在行动中没有合作过
Our paths never crossed on Copperhead,

12:16.150 --> 12:19.350
但是我确实和你的一个同事合作过
but I did deal with one of your colleagues;

12:19.420 --> 12:21.050
一个不太能干的中间人
a less-capable associate.

12:21.120 --> 12:24.120
他怎么了
Whatever happened to him?

12:24.180 --> 12:26.250
他已经从这个世界消失了
He was skinned and hung from an overpass.

12:26.320 --> 12:28.850
我想起来了
Oh, yes, I recall.

12:28.920 --> 12:31.420
他没有在保证的时间内把东西送到
He couldn't deliver on promises made.

12:31.480 --> 12:34.080
你也可能会想起  他是我的前任
You may also recall that he was my predecessor.

12:34.150 --> 12:36.180
我参加行动后  你得到了你想要的
When I joined Copperhead, you got what you wanted.

12:36.250 --> 12:37.520
我也会得到"锡拉"
You'll get Scylla, too.

12:37.580 --> 12:40.350
如果我拿不到
If I don't,

12:40.420 --> 12:43.780
我就扒了你的皮
I'll peel you like a wet grape.

12:43.850 --> 12:46.220
报酬是100
And the price is 100.

12:46.280 --> 12:47.580
150
150.

12:47.650 --> 12:51.820
125  别让我失望
125. Don't disappoint me.

12:58.220 --> 13:03.380
你们说的  125
Well, 125...

13:03.450 --> 13:04.150
再乘1百万
Million.

13:06.780 --> 13:08.920
苏珊  格雷琴  不管你名字是什么
Susan, Gretchen, whatever your name is,

13:08.980 --> 13:11.320
我建议你赶快找个方法
I suggest you find a way to bury the hatchet

13:11.380 --> 13:13.820
和迈克尔·斯科菲尔德的女人和解
with Michael Scofield's woman.

13:13.880 --> 13:15.980
我们有的忙了
We got work to do.

13:25.220 --> 13:29.120
我怎么觉得有人早上起来
Why do I get the feeling that some poor bastard woke up

13:29.180 --> 13:30.450
会发现自己的车没了
to an empty driveway this morning?

