不  算了
No, you know what? You know, no.

27:50.290 --> 27:52.820
打电话给Self  我回
Call Self, okay, because... because I'm gonna go back

27:52.890 --> 27:53.990
-监狱去  -好了
to the can. I'm done with this... All right.

27:54.050 --> 27:56.550
冷静点  冷静点
Just calm down. Calm down.

27:56.620 --> 27:58.220
我要你查一下
I want you to look up

27:58.290 --> 28:00.020
帝王大道和威洛斯大道街角的
all the local businesses at the corner

28:00.090 --> 28:01.520
所有地方企业
of King and Willow.

28:01.590 --> 28:03.320
我要外部装有安全摄像的
I need the ones with exterior security cameras,

28:03.390 --> 28:04.850
因为我要查个车牌号
'cause I'm looking for a license plate number,

28:04.920 --> 28:06.590
好吗
all right?

28:09.550 --> 28:11.720
为什么不道歉
How about an apology?

28:19.590 --> 28:20.920
斯科菲尔德去哪了
Where the hell is Scofield?

28:20.990 --> 28:22.650
我们全等着他破土动工
We've been waiting for him to break ground all day.

28:22.720 --> 28:24.590
他还要处理最后一件事
He's taking care of one last thing.

28:24.650 --> 28:25.820
早上他会来找你
He'll be here in the morning.

28:25.890 --> 28:27.820
莎拉呢  她对会面作何回应
And Sara, what'd she say about our meeting?

28:27.890 --> 28:29.890
她说没兴趣
She's not interested.

28:29.950 --> 28:31.550
行  如果她改变注意  我会在那等她
Okay, well, if she changes her mind, I'll be there.

28:31.620 --> 28:33.090
只想让大家都知道
Just so everyone knows,

28:33.150 --> 28:35.650
这是莎拉做了结的最后机会
this is Sara's last chance to settle up.

28:35.720 --> 28:37.150
我想让大家开诚布公
I want all the grievances out on the table

28:37.220 --> 28:38.190
这样我们才能继续合作
so we can move forward.

28:39.620 --> 28:42.190
听清楚了  美女
Listen to me, skank.

28:42.250 --> 28:43.250
你只是被
You just got your stripes

28:43.320 --> 28:44.920
你的旧老板甩掉的鸟人
ripped off your sleeve by your old boss.

28:44.990 --> 28:47.220
