So whatever clout you had with the Company,

28:47.290 --> 28:48.220
现在都没了
it's gone.

28:48.290 --> 28:49.920
你现在是我的手下
You work for me now.

28:49.990 --> 28:53.520
所以  你在这个乡巴佬面前怎么摆架子都行
So you can try to pull rank on the hick here all you want,

28:53.590 --> 28:55.250
但别把我的耐心当弱点
but don't mistake my patience for weakness.

28:55.320 --> 28:57.620
你还活着只有一个理由
You're alive right now for one reason:

28:57.690 --> 28:59.420
就是我允许你活着
because I'm allowing you to be.

28:59.490 --> 29:00.850
一旦把锡拉弄到手
So when I get Scylla,

29:00.920 --> 29:02.420
你就可以拿到你的报酬
you'll get your traveling money.

29:02.490 --> 29:03.420
而这一切都结束后
And when this is over,

29:03.490 --> 29:05.250
你要是胆敢踏进
if you step one foot

29:05.320 --> 29:07.450
美国半步  我会用
on American soil, I'm gonna take

29:07.520 --> 29:09.790
这把枪...
this gun...

29:09.850 --> 29:12.050
用子弹在你这里
and I'm gonna put a bullet

29:12.120 --> 29:13.720
开个洞
right there.

29:17.450 --> 29:19.750
你也一样  乡巴佬
And that goes for you, too, Gummo.

29:19.820 --> 29:21.020
听清楚了吗
Are we clear?

29:21.090 --> 29:22.220
听清楚了
We're clear.

29:31.020 --> 29:32.750
给  我做的
Here. I made this.

29:32.820 --> 29:34.650
这个图表记录了
It's a chart of all

29:34.720 --> 29:36.050
所以进出这个办公室的人
the people coming in and out of the office,

29:36.120 --> 29:38.890
显示了哪天  什么时段是最忙的
showing which times of the day are the busiest

29:38.950 --> 29:41.320
以及什么时段可以挖掘
and which are best for digging.

29:42.850 --> 29:44.290
只管听电话就行
Just answer the phones.

29:49.890 --> 29:51.090
我会处理这个
I'll handle this.

29:56.790 --> 29:58.220
-拿到了吗  -等等
- Did you get it? - Hold on.

29:58.290 --> 29:59.850
赶快
Hurry up.

30:02.050 --> 30:03.090
为什么要
Why are we doing

30:03.150 --> 30:04.120
再做一次
this again?

30:04.190 --> 30:06.220
如果她想不付锡拉的账
It's an insurance policy.

30:06.290 --> 30:08.620
这就是我们的救命稻草
If she tries to get out of that big Scylla payday.

30:08.690 --> 30:10.520
有多少钱
How big of a payday?

30:10.590 --> 30:14.020
1百万美元
One million dollars.

30:18.150 --> 30:19.920
你如果再用枪指着我
You put a gun on me again,

30:19.990 --> 30:22.050
我就不会单单会把她的指纹复制下来
and these aren't the only set of prints I'll be copying.

30:22.120 --> 30:24.690
从现在开始  我们是盟友了
From this moment on, we are allies.

30:24.750 --> 30:25.820
她还在看我们吗
She watching?

30:25.890 --> 30:27.420
是的
Yes.

30:27.490 --> 30:28.990
撑着点
Brace yourself.

30:29.050 --> 30:29.990
干嘛
For what?

30:30.050 --> 30:34.190
没叫你  以后不准再踏进我办公室半步
Don't you ever come in my office again unless you're summoned!

30:41.750 --> 30:43.320
布伦斯在车上
Burrows was in the car.

30:43.390 --> 30:46.450
看来情报是可靠的
It appears our source is dependable.

30:46.520 --> 30:49.420
我说引蛇出洞  可不意味着用我做饵
When I said bait the hook, I did not mean with me.

30:49.490 --> 30:51.090
他们差一点就杀了我
They came that close to killing me.

30:51.150 --> 30:52.790
我不会让这种事情发生
I wouldn't let that happen.

30:54.250 --> 30:57.120
如果你不满意我的方法
But if you're unhappy with my methods,

30:57.190 --> 30:59.850
你大可以让别人来做
maybe you should parcel out the job to someone else.

30:59.920 --> 31:02.020
我不接受辞呈
I don't accept resignations.

31:02.090 --> 31:03.790
和神秘人达成协议
Close the deal with the mystery man

31:03.850 --> 31:05.220
今天就把俩兄弟给我抓回来
and bring the brothers to me today

31:05.290 --> 31:07.620
否则你的解雇金就会变成运尸袋
or your severence pay will be a body bag.

31:07.690 --> 31:11.350
光天化日  在大街上  他们知道你的路线
Broad daylight, city street, and they knew your route.

31:11.420 --> 31:14.920
如果斯科菲尔德的任务是想杀你
If Scofield's mission was to kill you,

31:14.990 --> 31:17.490
他会用更好的办法
he'd have a better way to do it.

31:24.020 --> 31:26.350
-还要其他东西吗  -不用
Sara, you have everything you need? No.

31:26.420 --> 31:27.550
没事
I'm good.

31:28.420 --> 31:31.160
一切顺利  好了
Everything's just fine.Alright.

31:32.750 --> 31:34.550
快好了  费尔南多
Almost done, Fernando.

31:36.640 --> 31:37.960
可以了
Now you go.

31:39.950 --> 31:42.420
医生  如果不是你的话 我就死在这桌子上了
I would've died on this table if it weren't for you, Doc.

31:42.490 --> 31:44.220
我会等你付诊金的
Mm-hmm. Just wait till you get my bill.

31:44.290 --> 31:45.720
撑着点  苏克雷
Hang in there, Sucre.

31:45.790 --> 31:48.220
就算"公司"还不知道这个仓库
Even if the warehouse ain't on the Company's radar,

31:48.290 --> 31:49.350
我们很清楚被发现后的结果
we sure as hell are.

31:49.420 --> 31:52.390
-这事完了  -你说不准
This job's over. You don't know that.

31:52.450 --> 31:54.050
我只知道  我不想回福克斯河监狱
I ain't going back to Fox River, I know that.

31:54.120 --> 31:55.520
你觉得赛尔夫发现公司把我们弄成这样
What do you think Self is gonna do

31:55.590 --> 31:57.390
他会怎么做
when he finds out the Company made us?

31:58.790 --> 32:00.150
我们很快就会知道
We're about to find out.

32:00.220 --> 32:01.490
喂
Yeah?

32:01.550 --> 32:03.050
罗兰在哪
Hey, where the hell is Roland?

32:03.120 --> 32:05.090
他的全球定位掉线了
His GPS just went offline.

32:17.840 --> 32:20.500
我到了
I'm here.

32:44.420 --> 32:45.420
怎样
Well?

32:45.490 --> 32:47.190
开丰田走了
Took the Corolla.

32:48.920 --> 32:51.690
-把他的手提也带了吗  -是的
Take his laptop, too? Yeah.

32:51.750 --> 32:53.150
阿历克斯
Alex.

33:02.720 --> 33:04.120
你还好吗
You doing okay?

33:04.190 --> 33:06.050
-医生  还要多久  -快了
How much longer,doc? Almost.

33:07.120 --> 33:09.220
你能处理这些吗
Hey, you got this covered?

33:09.290 --> 33:11.620
你们还在这干什么
What are you still doing here?

33:11.690 --> 33:13.490
去把那兔崽子抓回来
Go get the son of a bitch.

33:17.550 --> 33:19.020
行了
All done.

34:20.090 --> 34:21.720
把钱带来了吗
You got my money?

34:23.420 --> 34:26.590
我以为这是
Oh, yo, I thought this

34:26.650 --> 34:28.420
公平交易  对吧
was going to be a legit business transaction, okay?

34:28.490 --> 34:29.750
你不给我钱  我就不会
You don't got my money, I don't got

34:29.820 --> 34:33.290
-把俩兄弟的地址告诉你  -他们在哪
the location of the brothers. Where are they?

34:34.020 --> 34:35.250
天啊
Oh, God!

34:35.320 --> 34:37.890
你这是干什么
What are you doing?!

35:20.720 --> 35:22.020
莎拉
Sara...

35:29.820 --> 35:32.490
你好  莎拉
Hello, Sara.

35:39.720 --> 35:43.390
我以前的一个导师给我讲过一个故事
A former mentor of mine once told me a story

35:43.450 --> 35:45.450
我觉得很适合这个情况
that I think applies to this situation.

35:45.520 --> 35:47.030
内战结束时  格兰特的联军
At the end of the Civil War, Grant's Union Army

35:47.030 --> 35:51.450
在阿波马托克斯战胜李的联军
had Lee's Confederate soldiers outflanked at Appomattox.

35:51.520 --> 35:54.150
李明白更多流血事件的无益
Lee understood the futility of more bloodshed,

35:54.220 --> 35:56.090
所以他请求停战
so he requested a cease-fire.

35:56.150 --> 35:58.020
他想结束战争
He wanted to bring an end to the fighting.

35:58.090 --> 36:00.350
当天早上还在互相厮杀的士兵
Soldiers that had been killing each other that morning,

36:00.420 --> 36:02.250
下午首次穿过战线
walked across the lines that afternoon

36:02.320 --> 36:03.650
成为同盟
for the first time as allies

36:03.720 --> 36:06.320
互相交换北方的咖啡和南方的烟草
to trade Northern coffee for Southern tobacco.

36:06.390 --> 36:09.520
现在  我不期望我们互换礼品
Now, I don't expect us to exchange gifts,

36:09.590 --> 36:11.890
但不意味着我们不能成为盟友
but that doesn't mean we can't be allies.

36:20.790 --> 36:22.220
当然  你不会和解
Of course, you can't have a cease-fire

36:22.290 --> 36:23.320
除非双方
without both parties

36:23.390 --> 36:25.390
达到各自目的
getting what they want.

36:38.890 --> 36:40.590
你有5分钟
You have five minutes.

36:40.650 --> 36:43.720
随你尽管在我背上加伤疤
Put as many scars on my back as possible.

37:07.290 --> 37:10.450
我不想催你  但只剩4分钟了
I don't want to rush you, but you have four minutes left.

37:11.650 --> 37:13.050
她叫什么名字
What was her name?

37:13.120 --> 37:14.620
只有这一次机会  莎拉
This is a one-time deal, Sara.

37:14.690 --> 37:16.850
你要血债血还  现在就动手
You want your pound of flesh, you take it now.

37:16.920 --> 37:18.320
-她叫什么名字  -谁
What was her name? Who?

37:18.390 --> 37:19.650
看守的人
The guard--

37:19.720 --> 37:22.050
你射杀  死在我怀里的人
the one you shot and left to die in my arms.

37:22.120 --> 37:23.250
就为这个
That's what this is about?

37:23.320 --> 37:25.090
一个不尽职的看守人
A guard that couldn't do her job?

37:26.820 --> 37:29.490
她叫什么名字
What was her name?

37:38.020 --> 37:39.520
她叫什么名字
What was her name?

37:39.590 --> 37:41.920
泰勒
Taylor.

37:41.990 --> 37:43.690
她的姓呢
Her first name?

37:43.750 --> 37:46.190
米歇尔  我想
Michelle... I think.

37:47.450 --> 37:48.990
你应该清楚  这不是为我
You should know that this isn't about me.

37:49.050 --> 37:51.320
我能忍受你在我背上留的伤疤
I can handle the scars you put on my back,

37:51.390 --> 37:52.850
但你对米歇尔的作为
but what you did to Michelle...

37:52.920 --> 37:54.720
我得服从命令  她想帮你逃跑
I had orders. She tried to help you escape.

37:54.790 --> 37:56.720
她帮我逃脱了  她不是想
She did help me escape. She didn't try.

38:03.290 --> 38:05.020
莎拉
Sara...

38:12.950 --> 38:15.420
你只想着用她来杀鸡儆猴
You were too busy making an example out of her

38:15.490 --> 38:17.320
没想到找她留给我的钥匙
to find the key that she left with me.

38:17.390 --> 38:19.750
她也得到应有的惩罚了
Then she got what she deserved.

38:22.520 --> 38:26.090
她救了我
She saved my life.

38:27.250 --> 38:29.420
而你杀了她
And you took her's.

38:30.450 --> 38:33.620
你达到目的了
You proved your point.

38:33.690 --> 38:34.890
我们扯平了
We're even.

38:37.450 --> 38:40.090
我们还离扯平远着呢
We're a long way from even.

38:40.150 --> 38:42.390
等这个结束了  你会为米歇尔付出代价
And when this is over, you'll pay for Michelle.

38:48.490 --> 38:49.790
他们在哪
Where are they?

38:53.990 --> 38:58.350
在膝盖骨上中一枪
The thing about a gunshot to the kneecap--

38:58.420 --> 39:00.550
会过几天才能死
it takes days to die from it.

39:01.790 --> 39:03.950
现在  如果说  我在这里
Now, if I were to shoot you, let's say,

39:04.020 --> 39:05.090
开一枪
here...

39:05.150 --> 39:07.250
弹头会直接穿过你的身体
the hollow point would tumble through you

39:07.320 --> 39:10.150
在你的内脏留下炙热的裂片
leaving white-hot slivers in your insides,

39:10.220 --> 39:13.050
带给你难以想象的痛苦
causing unimaginable pain.

39:13.120 --> 39:16.490
直到你在这小道里流血而亡
Only ending when you bled out on this pavement.

39:16.550 --> 39:18.450
你不想这样吧
You don't want that, do you?

39:22.220 --> 39:24.820
告诉我他们兄弟在哪
Then tell me where the brothers are.

39:26.420 --> 39:28.490
他们在一个仓库里
They're in a warehouse.

39:28.550 --> 39:31.620
圣佩德罗30号码头  他们都在那
Pier 31, San Pedro-- they're all there.

39:31.690 --> 39:34.950
-求你  -谢谢
Please... Thank you.

39:36.520 --> 39:37.590
不
No!

39:37.650 --> 39:38.590
你在干嘛
What are you doing?!

39:38.650 --> 39:41.650
我说了你想知道的
I told you what you wanted...!

39:54.690 --> 39:56.490
不  不
No, no...

39:56.550 --> 39:57.990
不
No!

40:04.420 --> 40:06.690
好了  好了
All right, all right!

40:12.190 --> 40:13.990
你迟早有机会收拾他  退后
You'll get your shot. Now back off.

40:14.050 --> 40:15.690
阿历克斯  听他的
Alex, listen to him.

40:15.750 --> 40:18.050
你迟早有机会收拾他
Hey, hey, you'll get your shot, man.

40:18.120 --> 40:19.490
你迟早有机会收拾他
You'll get your shot.

40:20.720 --> 40:21.850
迈克尔  快走  他出卖了我们
Michael, come on. He sold us out.

40:21.920 --> 40:22.890
你在干嘛
What are you doing?

40:22.950 --> 40:24.450
我们得走了
We got to go.

40:49.390 --> 40:53.090
等等  等等
Wait... wait...

40:54.150 --> 40:56.190
等等
Wait...

40:56.250 --> 40:57.690
迈克尔  快走
Michael, let's go.

41:09.120 --> 41:13.290
别再给我说什么新消息
Don't hand me any more updates.

41:16.290 --> 41:17.790
他们在监视我了
They're surveilling me.

41:17.850 --> 41:20.720
他们在追杀我
They're coming after me.

41:21.920 --> 41:22.920
将军  我们会抓到他们的
General, we'll get them.

41:22.990 --> 41:25.090
这又不是第一次
This isn't the first time someone's

41:25.150 --> 41:26.350
有人想要你的命
made an attempt on your life.

41:26.420 --> 41:28.290
这次不是想要我的命
This is not an attempt on my life.

41:28.350 --> 41:31.090
这次是想得到我的卡
This is an attempt on my card.

41:35.020 --> 41:36.090
叫怀特来
Get Wyatt.

41:36.150 --> 41:37.220
我们正在联系他
We're trying to contact him.

41:37.290 --> 41:39.450
别只关顾着想  快把怀特叫来
Don't try anything-- just get Wyatt.

41:39.520 --> 41:41.120
你想怎么继续下去
How do you want to proceed?

41:41.190 --> 41:42.620
我要转移它
I want it moved.

41:42.690 --> 41:44.890
做必要的安全准备
To make the necessary arrangements for security

41:44.950 --> 41:46.050
要好几天
would take days.

41:46.120 --> 41:48.150
我不管有多困难
I don't care about logistics.

41:48.220 --> 41:50.090
我要转移它
I want it moved.

41:50.150 --> 41:51.890
转移锡拉
Move Scylla.

41:51.950 --> 41:53.590
现在
Now!

42:08.150 --> 42:10.650
对不起
I'm sorry...

42:12.590 --> 42:16.320
对不起  对不起
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

42:16.390 --> 42:18.050
我知道
I know.

42:18.120 --> 42:20.290
我知道
I know.

42:20.350 --> 42:24.650
我还不想死  兄弟
I'm not ready to go, man.
